11 An Act relating to public retirement systems;
amending 47 O.S. 2021, Section 2-300, as last amended
12 by Section 1, Chapter 361, O.S.L. 2024 (47 O.S. Supp.
2024, Section 2-300), which relates to the Oklahoma
13 Law Enforcement Retirement System; modifying term;
providing for participation of certain new employees
14 of certain agency in the Oklahoma Law Enforcement
Retirement System; providing for codification; and
15 declaring an emergency.
16
17
18
